enum ih::RobotOptionFlag

Options for the robot.

The options are used for configuring a RobotPlanningExecution and RobotGripper instance.

See Also
RobotPlanningExecution, RobotGripper
Enumerator
ROBOT_OPTION_NONE 

No option configured

ROBOT_OPTION_VERBOSE_INFO 

Outputs verbose information of the instance's actions

ROBOT_OPTION_DUMMY_ROBOT 

Makes the robot a dummy, so that no movement is executed
